### ================================================================
### Smart Parking — Policy Simulator Test Collection
### ================================================================
### Run with:
###   - VS Code REST Client extension
###   - Thunder Client
###   - curl (copy individual requests)
###
### Ensure backend is running: cd backend && node index.js
### ================================================================

@base = http://localhost:8000/api
@contentType = application/json

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 1. VIEW RULES
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 1a. GET /api/simulator/rules — View all rule configuration
GET {{base}}/simulator/rules

### Expected: 200, { success: true, rules: { occupancy, traffic, violations, ... }, priority_levels }


# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 2. SINGLE-AREA SIMULATIONS
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 2a. Low Occupancy — No action needed
POST {{base}}/simulator/run
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "area": "A",
  "occupancy": 35,
  "traffic": 40,
  "violations": 1,
  "capacity": 200
}

### Expected: 200, status "ok", occupancy_status "underutilized", suggestions include "suggest_load_shift"


### 2b. Optimal Range — Normal operation
POST {{base}}/simulator/run
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "area": "B",
  "occupancy": 70,
  "traffic": 80,
  "violations": 0,
  "capacity": 200
}

### Expected: 200, occupancy_status "optimal", efficiency_score > 0.3, no critical suggestions


### 2c. High Occupancy — Approaching capacity
POST {{base}}/simulator/run
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "area": "A",
  "occupancy": 88,
  "traffic": 150,
  "violations": 3,
  "capacity": 200,
  "vehicles_entering": 25,
  "vehicles_leaving": 10
}

### Expected: 200, occupancy_status "high", action "prepare_reroute", efficiency_score low


### 2d. Full Capacity — Immediate reroute
POST {{base}}/simulator/run
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "area": "C",
  "occupancy": 97,
  "traffic": 200,
  "violations": 5,
  "capacity": 200,
  "avg_speed_kmh": 12
}

### Expected: 200, occupancy_status "full", action "reroute_immediately", bottleneck detected, low speed flagged


### 2e. With Slot Details — Granular evaluation
POST {{base}}/simulator/run
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "area": "A",
  "occupancy": 65,
  "traffic": 90,
  "violations": 2,
  "capacity": 200,
  "slot_details": [
    { "slot_id": "A-001", "is_occupied": true, "vehicle_type": "car" },
    { "slot_id": "A-002", "is_occupied": true, "vehicle_type": "motorcycle" },
    { "slot_id": "A-003", "is_occupied": false },
    { "slot_id": "A-004", "is_occupied": true, "vehicle_type": "car" },
    { "slot_id": "A-005", "is_occupied": false }
  ]
}

### Expected: 200, slot_evaluation with vehicle_breakdown, occupancy_status "moderate"


# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 3. MULTI-AREA SIMULATION — Load Balancing
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 3a. Three areas — One overloaded, one underutilized
POST {{base}}/simulator/run
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "areas": [
    {
      "area": "A",
      "area_id": "a1",
      "occupancy_percent": 92,
      "capacity": 250,
      "traffic_volume": 200,
      "vehicles_entering": 30,
      "vehicles_leaving": 10,
      "violations": { "count": 4 }
    },
    {
      "area": "B",
      "area_id": "b1",
      "occupancy_percent": 45,
      "capacity": 300,
      "traffic_volume": 80,
      "violations": { "count": 1 }
    },
    {
      "area": "C",
      "area_id": "c1",
      "occupancy_percent": 60,
      "capacity": 180,
      "traffic_volume": 90,
      "violations": { "count": 0 }
    }
  ]
}

### Expected: 200, system_status "warning" or "imbalanced", reroute suggestions from A to B, balance suggestions


### 3b. All areas critical — System-wide overload
POST {{base}}/simulator/run
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "areas": [
    { "area": "A", "area_id": "a1", "occupancy_percent": 96, "capacity": 200, "traffic_volume": 195, "violations": { "count": 8 } },
    { "area": "B", "area_id": "b1", "occupancy_percent": 94, "capacity": 200, "traffic_volume": 190, "violations": { "count": 6 } },
    { "area": "C", "area_id": "c1", "occupancy_percent": 91, "capacity": 200, "traffic_volume": 185, "violations": { "count": 5 } }
  ]
}

### Expected: 200, system_status "critical", no available alternatives, enforcement flags


# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 4. POLICY TESTING
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 4a. Dynamic Pricing — Test price increase impact
POST {{base}}/simulator/policy-test
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "policy_type": "dynamic_pricing",
  "current_state": {
    "occupancy_percent": 88,
    "traffic_volume": 160,
    "violations": 5,
    "capacity": 200
  },
  "policy_params": {
    "price_increase_percent": 30
  }
}

### Expected: 200, simulated_state with lower occupancy, efficiency_change positive


### 4b. Time Limit — Restrict max duration
POST {{base}}/simulator/policy-test
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "policy_type": "time_limit",
  "current_state": {
    "occupancy_percent": 75,
    "traffic_volume": 120,
    "violations": 3,
    "capacity": 200
  },
  "policy_params": {
    "max_duration_minutes": 90
  }
}

### Expected: 200, simulated occupancy reduced, traffic increased (more turnover)


### 4c. Reserved Zones — Allocate reserved parking
POST {{base}}/simulator/policy-test
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "policy_type": "reserved_zones",
  "current_state": {
    "occupancy_percent": 70,
    "traffic_volume": 140,
    "violations": 2,
    "capacity": 200
  },
  "policy_params": {
    "reserved_percent": 15
  }
}

### Expected: 200, effective capacity reduced, occupancy recalculated higher


### 4d. Enforcement Boost — Increase patrol frequency
POST {{base}}/simulator/policy-test
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "policy_type": "enforcement_boost",
  "current_state": {
    "occupancy_percent": 60,
    "traffic_volume": 100,
    "violations": 8,
    "capacity": 200
  },
  "policy_params": {
    "patrol_increase_percent": 75
  }
}

### Expected: 200, violations reduced significantly, efficiency improved


### 4e. Active Reroute — Redirect incoming traffic
POST {{base}}/simulator/policy-test
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "policy_type": "reroute_active",
  "current_state": {
    "occupancy_percent": 92,
    "traffic_volume": 180,
    "violations": 4,
    "capacity": 200
  },
  "policy_params": {
    "reroute_percent": 20
  }
}

### Expected: 200, occupancy drops to ~72%, traffic drops, efficiency improves


# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 5. ERROR HANDLING
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 5a. Empty body → 400
POST {{base}}/simulator/run
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### Expected: 400, error message


### 5b. Missing area → 400
POST {{base}}/simulator/run
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "occupancy": 50
}

### Expected: 400, error about missing "area"


### 5c. Invalid occupancy (> 100) → 400
POST {{base}}/simulator/run
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "area": "A",
  "occupancy": 150,
  "traffic": 100
}

### Expected: 400, error about occupancy range


### 5d. Missing policy_type → 400
POST {{base}}/simulator/policy-test
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "current_state": { "occupancy_percent": 50 }
}

### Expected: 400, error about missing policy_type


### 5e. Unknown policy type → handled gracefully
POST {{base}}/simulator/policy-test
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "policy_type": "teleport_vehicles",
  "current_state": { "occupancy_percent": 50, "traffic_volume": 100, "violations": 0, "capacity": 200 }
}

### Expected: 200, message about unknown policy type, no changes applied
